Today’s ‘Wordle’ #1166 Hints, Clues And Answer For Wednesday, August 28th

Looking for help with today's New York Times Wordle? Here are hints, clues and commentary to help you solve today's Wordle and sharpen your guessing game.

SpaceX Starship Flotillas Could Outrace NASA To Create Moon Base Alpha

SpaceX, with its rapidly expanding squadron of Starship rockets and super-capsules, is set to speed past NASA in creating humanity’s first celestial citadel on the Moon.

Cine, Nwangwu Fail To Make Vikings Roster, But QB Jaren Hall Earns Spot

The Minnesota Vikings have finalized their 53-man roster, and the decision to cut a productive returner and a former first-round choice are among the most notable moves.

Fans Unite To Keep Kelly Monaco On ‘General Hospital’

The fans of "General Hospital" are uniting to keep Kelly Monaco on the veteran abc daytime drama.

Stored And Inspected: Turkey’s Latest Reported S-400 Proposal Isn’t New

The alleged Turkish offer to keep S-400s in storage with an inspection arrangement suggests Ankara wants to meet Washington halfway.

NFL Opens Door For Private Equity Ownership Stakes: Here’s What That Means

Up to 10% of each NFL team can be owned by private equity firms under the approved agreement.

FC Barcelona MVP Olmo Beams About ‘Unbeatable’ Rayo Vallecano Debut And Is Hailed By Pedri

New FC Barcelona signing Dani Olmo beamed about an "unbeatable" scoring MVP debut against Rayo Vallecano on Tuesday and was also hailed by teammate Pedri.

Northern Lights Alert: Aurora Borealis May Make Another Appearance In Northern States

People in areas with clear forecasts and minimal light pollution will have the most suitable viewing conditions.

FC Barcelona Coach Flick Says Team Not Happy With ‘Sad’ Rayo Victory And Reveals Serious Injury

Speaking to DAZN, FC Barcelona head coach Hansi Flick lamented a "sad" victory over Rayo Vallecano on Tuesday which he confirmed has brought with it a serious injury.

Dana White’s Contender Series - Season 8, Week 3 Results: Winners & Losers

Everything you need to know about tonight's Season 8 Episode 3 Dana White's Contender Series Fight Card. Results, reactions, contract winners, winners, losers and more.

Harris And Walz Plan First Formal Joint Interview—Airing Thursday On CNN

Vice President Kamala Harris has largely avoided questions from the media since President Joe Biden ended his reelection bid.

Who Is Shadow The Hedgehog In The ‘Sonic 3’ Trailer?

Shadow the Hedgehog appears in the new trailer for Sonic the Hedgehog 3, voiced by Keanu Reeves, but who is Sonic's powerful new rival?

Box Office Flop ‘Borderlands’ Debuts On Digital Streaming This Week

"Borderlands"—the movie adaptation of the hit video game that bombed in theaters in early August—is coming to digital streaming this week.

NFL And Peacock: The Shift From Traditional TV To Streaming For Sports

Discover how Peacock is influencing NFL broadcasting and the impact of streaming services on sports. Explore the 2024 NFL opening week schedule and key games.

What’s Ahead For Cam Whitmore In 2024-2025?

Cam Whitmore was one of the pleasant surprises for the Rockets in 2023-2024 in what was overall a surprise season. Can he build on it?
